{"word":"G4716 - σταυρός - staurós - stow-ros' - Cross","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σταυρός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">staurós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">stow-ros'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cross</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"சிலுவை - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. an upright stake"},{"paragraph":"2. a cross"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the base of <a href=\"#/G2476 - ἵστημι - hístēmi - his'-tay-mee/2476\">G2476</a>; a <i>stake</i> or <i>post</i> (as <i>set</i> upright), that is, (specifically) a <i>pole</i> or <i>cross</i> (as an instrument of capital punishment); figuratively <i>exposure to death</i>, that is, <i>self denial</i>; by implication the <i>atonement</i> of Christ: - cross.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G388/388\">G388</a>, <a href=\"#/G4617/4617\">G4617</a>, <a href=\"#/G4716/4716\">G4716</a>"}]}